Mail::Vacation version 0.01
=====================

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

USAGE

You should probably modify the 'conf/*.conf' entries for your own installation.

Also each script (*.pl) will want to be pointed to the correct config file.

DOCS

For more info see 'perldoc Mail::Vacation'

DEPENDENCIES

See Makefile.PL

